Other names: Blue Investment Baia Wind Farm

Baia Blue Planet wind farm is a wind farm in Baia, Tulcea County, Northern Dobruja, Romania.

Project Details

Table 1: Phase-level project details for Baia Blue Planet wind farm

Phase name Status Nameplate capacity Type Owner 1 Cancelled (inferred January 2023) 35 MW[1] Onshore[2] Blue Investment Partners [100%][3]
